## Plan Summary

**Objective:** Add real tmux integration testing to prevent shipping broken GUI layouts.

**Key Change:** Build and Teach phases run in parallel (no dependency between them).
Test phase depends on both Build (needs --dry-run flag) and Teach (guidance should be
updated before writing new tests that follow the guidance).

**Phases:**

1. **Build** - Add `--dry-run` flag to orchestrate, fix inplace layout `-p` flags
2. **Teach** - Update guidance to mandate real CLI smoke tests (runs parallel with Build)
3. **Test** - 13 real tmux integration tests across 2 files, zero mocking
4. **UAT** - Validate real tmux GUI end-to-end including full live launch
